data.description: 2 homes for the price of 1!! Discover the charm of this single-level home nestled on a corner lot! A fully fenced property, displaying a front porch and a gated carport parking space. Inviting interior boasts a sizable living room, vaulted ceilings, neutral paint, wood-tile flooring, and abundant natural light. The large eat-in kitchen offers SS gas range & microwave, quartz counters, stylish backsplash, recessed lighting, and white shaker cabinetry. Bedrooms are perfectly sized! Out the back, you have covered & open patios, BBQ grilling area, and so much room for your creative ideas to make it a complete outdoor living space. PLUS! This gem also has a detached guest quarter with a closet & private bathroom for added comfort. The RV gate enhances the home's practicality.
